Module vpm.gui_prototype
Package vpm.gui_prototype.models.PetStuff

Class Pet

java.lang.Object
vpm.gui_prototype.models.PetStuff.Pet
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPet
Direct Known Subclasses:
Bird, Cat, Dog, Fish
public abstract class Pet extends Object implements IPet
Abstract class representing a Pet in the system. This class contains common properties and behaviors for all pets.
